sub_title: Director Growth & Transformation Global E-Business (B2B eCommerce) at The HEINEKEN Company
summary:
Global Sales and business transformation leader with 15 years of a broad international experience in shaping and executing commercial and digital strategies.

Experience in numbers & bullets:
▹15 years+ in Sales & Business development
▹15 years+ in FMCG (2 multinational companies)
▹12 years+ in People development (led teams of 100+)
▹10 different roles
(from local entry level to global senior management)
▹10 years+ of International career
(worked & lived in 5 countries)
▹8 years+ in Management teams
(in 2 operating companies and in Global HQ)
▹4 years+ in Business (Digital) Transformation leveraging Tech & Data

Experience includes:
▹Managing P&L / Sales / Trade Marketing / Distributors
▹Change Management
▹Business transformation through Tech & Data
▹Building greenfield operation
▹Merging businesses after M&A
▹Building high performing teams
▹Designing & Implementing Route to Market models
▹Shaping new capabilities / frameworks / models
▹Leading global & cross-functional projects/teams
